  "texts": [
    "It deals with data extraction and analysis (Idri et al. 2016).",
    "To lessen the threat of imprecise or erroneous \"data extraction\", the form was completed independently by the two authors.",
    "Disagreements or doubts were settled by in-depth team discussions (AI and FI) to establish inter-rater reliability.",
    "In this systematic review of all DM-ML/ GYN oncology, we found 3499 candidate articles.",
    "181 of which fulfilled eligibility criteria, were in-depth analyzed to provide valuable insights."
  ]
}